userInput: The Eternal Quest: A knight kneels before a mystical lake, gazing at a sword jutting from the water, its blade glowing faintly. Mist rolls across the surface, hiding what lies beyond.
Through the Rift: Two adventurers stand at the edge of a glowing portal, their faces lit with awe. On the other side lies a world of floating islands, shimmering skies, and creatures unknown.
The Shattered Kingdom: An abandoned throne sits atop a crumbled dais in a ruined castle. The banners of a fallen empire flutter in the wind, with the distant mountains hiding dark secrets.
